original_title: Mon Ostéo a des Gros Seins
overview: Experience the colorful daily life of an osteopath's practice like no other! Cléa Gaultier and Tiffany Leiddi are osteopaths. But they have something else in common: a beautiful and very generous chest! And this is not to displease their clients. Some might even be tempted to come just to admire the view... It must be said that in addition to being professionals, the girls know how to give of themselves so that each patient leaves satisfied, no matter what their needs are!
title: My Osteopath Has Big Tits
